  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CReboot\uFF1E (Unsuspend this Digimon during your
    opponent's unsuspend phase.)[When Digivolving] Reveal 1 card from the top of
    your deck for each Digimon your opponent has in play. You may play 1 black or
    red Digimon card with a level of 5 or less among them without paying its memory
    cost. Place the remaining cards at the bottom of your deck in any order."
